Zimbabwe Finance Ministry Suspends Afre, Rainbow Trade

-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-05-12T14:01:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/zimbabwe-finance-ministry-suspends-afre-rainbow-trade-correct-.html
(Corrects spelling of spokesman’s name in first paragraph.)  Zimbabwe’s finance ministry suspended
trading of shares in Afre Ltd. and  Rainbow Tourism Group (RTG)  on the
nation’s bourse, without providing a reason, stock exchange
spokesman Robert Mubaiwa said by phone today from the capital,
Harare.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Durban,  South Africa  at 
